\begin{cases}
ax^2 & \text{if } x \geq a,\\
ax +2a& \text{if } x <a,
\end{cases}
\]कुनै एक रेखालाई प्रत्येक तेर्सो रेखालाई कम्तिमा एक पटक काट्ने गरी $a$ को सबैभन्दा ठूलो मान कति हो?  \[ \text{Solution:} \]  \[ \text{If } x \geq a, \]then $f(x) = ax^2$ is a parabola that opens upwards.  \[ \text{If } x < a, \]then $f(x) = ax + 2a$ is a line with slope $a$.  \[ \text{For } f(x) \text{ to be continuous at } x = a, \]the parabola and the line must have the same $y$-coordinate at $x = a$.  \[ \text{Thus, } a^3 = a^2 + 2a. \]This equation factors as $a(a - 2)(a + 1) = 0$, so $a = 0, 2, -1$.  \[ \text{If } a = 0, \]then $f(x) = 0$ for all $x$, so the graph of $f(x)$ is a horizontal line.  \[ \text{If } a = 2, \]then $f(x) = 2x^2$ for $x \geq 2$ and $f(x) = 2x + 4$ for $x < 2$.  \[ \text{If } a = -1, \]then $f(x) = -x^2$ for $x \geq -1$ and $f(x) = -x - 2$ for $x < -1$.  \[ \text{Thus, the only possible values of } a \text{ are } \boxed{2 \text{ and } -1}. \]

